description.narrative: UNICEF has established a fundraising and partnership strategy to work strategically with the private sector i.e. corporates, high net worth and private foundations in Egypt, with a target of raising $15million by the end of the CPD and creating partnerships that achieve results for children. In 2019, UNICEF raised 1.5 Million for Programs mainly from corporates like Allianz, Unilever and Hilton and High networth, Sawiris through their family foundation. This was against an annual target of $2million. UNICEF, in 2019 leveraged non-financial business for results partnerships of $1million to support cause frame work campaigns, advocacy and behavior change.. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:15/01/2020
